架車勁長同闊<br />\n要勁大個位先泊到<br />\n咪錶s位都泊唔到<br />\n因為仲要預埋開尾門距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d328566d96080d9cb6f6833f3b162b6ab4c5a5","tid":1329332,"uid":16827,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:55:23.000Z","msg":"以為自己開緊post<br />\n<br />\n利申：P 牌，買左車幾日<br />\n<br />\n阻住後車已經心理壓力大，快快手泊又驚撞到後面架車...自己花都唔緊要，撞花人地，都唔知要陪幾多個下先心理壓力大<br />\n<br />\n有冇師兄分享下點樣刻服有後車跟尾、又未熟泊車技巧時淆底既心態，話就話練多d 就得，但唔通下下搏撞花後面部車去練咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7da301ab4ab93cbcf17b3ca268d199be075f8f6","tid":1329332,"uid":280431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:04:54.000Z","msg":"搵個少人少車嘅地方練，亂得多就會熟，熟就會快"},{"pid":"8900e57ce7b79d838d76a7e6f871faa6c2a24f51","tid":1329332,"uid":121005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"咁考黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d5d8af5ddf0ada44654b594e802c17462c8ef6","tid":1329332,"uid":176392,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"fe327da45f33d7a8b2774bbc29224abd9b99bf48","tid":1329332,"uid":201604,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"係揸車 唔係開車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:15:35.000Z","msg":"係揸車 唔係開車"},{"pid":"bf3496bd688af2ade06a21dffcafb86a29213798","tid":1329332,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1296997ae8e4ce136818d2c2910a9eb35cc9db0","tid":1329332,"uid":119385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"82647679a289552b53fab5fc4ad7e628a8cbb5f4","tid":1329332,"uid":13084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"practice makes perfect"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:25:33.000Z","msg":"撞一下就欠一世債"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"驚咪買全保囉"},{"pid":"beb7570b03734a3b2c5646bf3f273690215f076e","tid":1329332,"uid":51041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cited